quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  3,122,"Apo mapoka maviri kubva pakati penyu vakanga vava pedyo nekurasa moyo, asi Allah vakanga varipo semubatsiri wavo. Uye vatendi vanofanirwa kupa chivimbo chavo kuna Allah"
  3,123,"Uye zvirokwazvo Allah vakakuitai kuti muve vakundi kuBadr, pamakanga muri vashoma musina simba. Naizvozvo ityai Allah zvakanyanya zvimwe mungava munotenda"
  3,124,"Rangarira (Muhammad (SAW)) apo pawakati kuvatendi: “Hazvikukwanirei here kuti Tenzi venyu vakubatsirei nezviuru zvitatu zvengirozi dzatumwa kubva kudenga?”"
  3,125,"“Hongu, kana mukatsungirira pamwe nekutya Allah, uye muvengi akauya kwamuri achimhanya, Tenzi venyu vachakubatsirai nezviuru zvishanu zvengirozi dzine rupau.”"
  3,126,"Uye Allah havana kunge vazviita asi seshoko rakanaka kwamuri uye senzira yekudzikamisa hana dzenyu nayo. Uye hakuna kukunda asi kubva kuna Allah, samasimba, vazere nehungwaru"
  3,127,"Kuti vabvise boka reavo vasina kutenda, kana kuvabuditsa pachena nekuvadzikisira, nekudaro vova vakundikani"
  3,128,"Kwauri (Muhammad (SAW)) hakuna mhereredzo; kana kuti Allah vakada vachavaregerera kana kuvaranga. Zvirokwazvo, ndivo vatadzi"
  3,129,"Uye Allah ndivo muridzi wezvese zviri kumatenga uye zvese zviri pasi. Vanoregerera uyo wavada, uye vanoranga uyo wavada. Uye Allah vanoregerera zvikuru, vane tsitsi dzakanyanya"
  3,130,"Imi vanotenda! Musava munodya chimbadzo chakapetwa kaviri kana kakawanda, asi ityai Allah kuti muve munobudirira"
  3,131,"Uye ityai moto, wakagadzirirwa avo vasingatendi"
  3,132,Uye teererai Allah nemutumwa (Muhammad (SAW)) kuti muve munowana tsitsi